values:
today i found out I MADE KICKLINE!!!!! I am so happy most of my friends made it too so im so happy i cant wait till all the practices start .... they start tomorrow and I'm so happy i made it!

i was jumpin around all day like a loozer...o well!

COMMENT!

xo Alaina xo

Yesterday I had kickline try-outs and our group did so good!!! 
I'm so happy...

I was really really nervous right before I went in I felt like I was ganna pee in my pants (dont worry i didnt) but then once I started I  was having so much fun!

Our group didnt get to try-out until about 6:00 because of our numbers I was 45 janie was 44 kellie was 46 and victoria was 47

I dont find out til monday if I made the team so I guess we'll have to wait nd see !


*Ti, thanks for helping me with everything during the summer and during try-outs you really helped me alot..dont know what I would do without ya!! Nd...later you're telling me why you were feelin so crappy the other day!


xo Alaina xo

Today I had kickline and it went pretty good!

I know the dance so I'm really happy but I was really tired sweaty and hot.

Our group does pretty good with the dance we're trying so hard so hopefully all the hard work wil pay off!

I'm so exciting for try-outs fri. I'm so ready!!

My group is going to practice and my friend kel's house tomorrow or at jessica's (she helps us with the dance)



I'm so excited I just want that day to be here!!!




Thats it for now....


xo Alaina xo  (p.s. did I mention that I'm really excited?)

I'm so happy its fall!  I love the smell and how the air is so crisp! Yay!

Kickline try-outs start tomorrow! I'm really excited but I'm really scared too I've never been on the team beftore . I'm also a little upset because my friend came over today and we were practicing and I hurt my knee so hopefully I'll be better for tomorrow...

COMMENT!!!



xo Alaina xo

Yesterday I went to adventureland with my friends. I had a lot of fun! After that I went over my friends house and played manhunt with a bunch of other people but everyone started to argue and talk gossip and it was sooo annoying..so I stopped playing. The rest of the night everyone was just talking telling secrets and stuff ... me and caroline were like the only ones who were getting kinda annoyed.But w/e its all in the past and everyone left still as friends!

Kelsey and Ally you to pretending to fight was hilarious!



Right now im just really tired so that means I'll post later




xo Alaina xo

Me and my friend are callin z100 tryin to win some cool stuff..we're havin bad luck :( ... lol
 
I'm goin to adventureland tomorrow with my friends and I'm excited!

Kickline try-outs start monday and I'm really nervous

sO thats it for now...I'll post later

COMMENT!!







xo AlaiNa xo
